%N A164919 Number of simple connected cubic nonhamiltonian graphs on 2n nodes.
%H A164919 F. C. Bussemaker, S. Cobeljic, L. M. Cvetkovic and J. J. Seidel, <a href="http://alexandria.tue.nl/repository/books/252909.pdf">Computer investigations of cubic graphs</a>, T.H.-Report 76-WSK-01, Technological University Eindhoven, Dept. Mathematics, 1976 [From _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jan 12 2012].
